Class AndroidSerializationInstantiator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.objenesis.instantiator.android.AndroidSerializationInstantiator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ObjectInstantiator

    public class AndroidSerializationInstantiator
extends Object
implements ObjectInstantiator
    ObjectInstantiator for Android which creates objects using the constructor from the first non-serializable parent class constructor, using internal methods on the Dalvik implementation of ObjectStreamClass.
    Author:
    Ian Parkinson (Google Inc.)
